      "span_text": "A nanodelivery system could be functionalized with a suitable tracer or present size-related properties that can be monitored in vivo to determine if it has reached its target. This could be an early indicator of the success or failure of a targeted drug delivery system and could shorten trials and regulatory trails [CITATION_1] ."
